Lookarounds

Thre is lookahead and lookbehind    

Lookaraouns turns to be the searching of metacharacters to find something behind or after a word.
like this 

silly cat
happy cat
cool cat
cool dog
cool bird
cool fish
fun cat

lookahead
Command -> (?<=cool\ )cat - With this I´m maching the words that have cool before cat in the text above.
Coomand -> (?<!cool\ )cat - With this I´m matching the words that dosen´t have cool before cat in the sequence.

lookbehind
Commands -> cool(?=\ cat) - Looking for the cat after the cool word
Commands -> cool(?!\ cat) - Looking for the word diferent than cat after cool